description: These guys play hard on the field, but they make sure to save a little energy for the post-game celebration. And while they may play on different teams, after the whistle, everyone's a winner when they head back to the house. Carter Woods and Alex James enjoy the spoils of victory while Ryan Jordan and Johnny B prove how valuable they are in supportive roles. The key is that they all cum together to make sure no one is left out, and isn't that really what team sports is truly all about?Enjoy!
series: NDB - 4991 - Johnny B, Carter Woods, Ryan Jordan & Alex James
title: Ballin' Bros
